details:
ISO 9001:2015 certified. Custom manufacturer of pump impellers for agricultural industry. Made from EPDM, butyl, fluoroelastomer, fluorosilicone, natural rubber, neoprene, nitrile, NBR, HNBR, SBR, silicone, high tear strength silicone, TPR, TPU, TPE, thermoplastics and polyurethane. Hose are abrasion, acid, alcohol, alkali, oxidation, ozone, radiation, sunlight and water resistant. Capabilities include injection molding, die cutting and prototyping. Assembly and PTFE coating additional services are also provided. Lean manufacturing and Kaizen/5S capable. Meets Mil-Spec, ANSI, AS, ASME, ASTM, DOT, SAE and TS standards. FAA, FDA and CSA approved. NADCAP, Six Sigma and CE certified. RoHS and REACH Compliant. JIT delivery. Overseas sourcing options also offered.
